        &lt;input type=&#39;text&#39; id=&#39;age&#39; value=&quot;22&quot;&gt;
    &lt;form/&gt;

&lt;!-- end snippet --&gt;

If your data were of the following form (use the `name` in the same way you are using the `id` attribute) you could use [FormData](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/FormData) instead

&lt;!-- begin snippet: js hide: false console: true babel: false --&gt;

